I need you to create a professional, modern, and visually appealing website. Please follow these guidelines:
Design Requirements:

Use a clean, contemporary design with a professional color scheme that's easy on the eyes
Ensure the layout is fully responsive and looks great on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
Include smooth scrolling, subtle animations, and modern UI elements
Use a readable, professional font combination (consider pairing a sans-serif for headings with a clean body font)
Maintain consistent spacing, alignment, and visual hierarchy throughout

Structure:

Create a clear navigation menu that's easy to use
Include these key sections: Hero/Landing section, About, Services/Features, Testimonials/Portfolio (if applicable), Contact
Add a professional footer with relevant links and information
Ensure all sections flow logically and guide visitors through the content

Technical Requirements:

Write clean, semantic HTML5
Use modern CSS3 with flexbox/grid for layouts
Make it interactive with smooth JavaScript effects where appropriate
Optimize for fast loading times
Ensure accessibility standards are met
Make the code well-commented and easy to modify later

